go Devo, and it's also home to two high school teams and Fort Lewis College, which boasts one of the fastest collegiate bike racing programs in the country.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.9998618615750547, \"rank\": 0.00013815670622982826, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}, {\"begin\": 3022, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.029952944530835e-23, \"text\": \"Fort Lewis College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Lewis_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Durango\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"two high school teams\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest collegiate bike racing programs\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in Durango, bicyclists are bonafide celebrities-this past October the town held a citywidecelebration for hometown hero Sepp Kussafter he won the Vuelta a Espa\\u00f1a.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"score\": 0.9998618615750547, \"rank\": 0.00013815670622982826, \"text\": \"Durango\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durango\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bicyclists\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"bonafide celebrities\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"the town\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"a citywidecelebration\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"hometown hero Sepp Kussafter\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vuelta\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"a Espa\\u00f1a\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You look around and there are so many amazing peers and mentors,\\\" Amos says.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many amazing peers\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"mentors\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3354}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they show you that it's possible to break into the sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Durango's cycling culture and infrastructure provided an ideal incubator for Amos.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Durango's cycling culture\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3458}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"an ideal incubator\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His parents are recreational riders who relocated to the town from Arizona just two years before he was born.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"score\": 0.9999871087833172, \"rank\": 1.2524031423774396e-05, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His parents\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"recreational riders\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3551}, {\"ngram\": \"the town\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3577}]}, {