": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"climbs\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But on downhills-specifically on tricky, dangerous, and technical ones-Amos turned heads.\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"downhills\", \"from\": 4427, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"tricky, dangerous, and technical ones\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4495}, {\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Older riders know there are times to risk it and to take it easy on descents,\\\" Wells says.\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Older riders\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"descents\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"Wells\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Riley would just go for it every time no matter how gnarly it was and he seemed to come out OK.\\\" Wells taught Amos the basics of endurance training-rest, recover, repeat-and gradually increased his weekly riding miles.\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4604, \"end\": 4609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\", \"score\": 0.9984870148401341, \"rank\": 0.0015129913761136714, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wells\", \"from\": 4701, \"to\": 4706}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4718}, {\"ngram\": \"the basics\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance training-rest\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4756}, {\"ngram\": \", recover\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"his weekly riding miles\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He invited Amos onto the Tuesday Night Worlds ride and watched as Amos thrived in the hyper-competitive environment.\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4839}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tuesday Night Worlds ride\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4874}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4890, \"to\": 4894}, {\"ngram\": \"the hyper-competitive environment\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the ensuing two seasons Amos blossomed into a top racer in the region, state, and then nation.\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 5040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ensuing two seasons\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4974}, {\"ngram\": \"a top racer\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 5001}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5015}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 5017, \"to\": 5022}, {\"ngram\": \"then nation\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, at age 16, Amos won the junior national title in cross-country-he repeated the win in 2019.\", \"from\": 5041, \"to\": 5141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 5053, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5065}, {\"ngram\": \"the junior national title\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5095}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those results earned Amos the opportunities to compete overseas.\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those results\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5155}, {\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5167}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunities\", \"from\": 5168, \"to\": 5185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some kids have been training since they were ten and already have a plan-Riley was pretty raw,\\\" Wells says.\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some kids\", \"from\": 5209, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan-Riley\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"Wells\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But he was super gung-ho and learned really fast.\\\"\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"super gung-ho\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Top American mountain bikers often falter when they travel to Europe to compete in the sport's highest international series-the UCI World Cup.\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5374, \"end\": 5382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999793981262, \"rank\": 2.035711181839277e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5438}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's highest international series\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"the UCI World Cup\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition is fierce, the racing is elbow-to-elbow, and the courses often boast scary features, like sheer drop-offs and slippery roots.\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5528}, {\"ngram\": \"the racing\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5550}, {\"ngram\": \"elbow\", \"from\": 5554, \"to\": 5559}, {\"ngram\": \"elbow\", \"from\": 5563, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"the courses\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"scary features\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5612}, {\"ngram\": \"sheer drop-offs\", \"from\": 5619, \"to\": 5634}, {\"ngram\": \"slippery roots\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Racers must be physiologically strong in order to endure the strong tempo at the front of the field, but they must also be fearless for the tricky downhills.\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Racers\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5701}, {\"ngram\": \"the strong tempo\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 5745, \"to\": 5754}, {\"ngram\": \"the tricky downhills\", \"from\": 5791, \"to\": 5811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amos thrived.\", \"from\": 5814, \"to\": 5827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 5814, \"to\": 5818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After graduating to theEspoircompetition level-a category for up-and-coming riders under the age of 23-he became the first American man to win a World Cup round in the division during the 2023 season.\", \"from\": 5828, \"to\": 6028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5951, \"end\": 5959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999793981262, \"rank\": 2.035711181839277e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theEspoircompetition\", \"from\": 5848, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"a category\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5885}, {\"ngram\": \"up-and-coming riders\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 5917, \"to\": 5924}, {\"ngram\": \"a World Cup round\", \"from\": 5971, \"to\": 5988}, {\"ngram\": \"the division\", \"from\": 5992, \"to\": 6004}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 season\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2024 he swept the World Cup races in theEspoircategory, and the results earned him a place on the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 6029, \"to\": 6143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup races\", \"from\": 6046, \"to\": 6065}, {\"ngram\": \"theEspoircategory\", \"from\": 6069, \"to\": 6086}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 6092, \"to\": 6103}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 6115, \"to\": 6122}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amos credits his success internationally to the fearless mentality he's developed alongside his cadre of up-and-coming American racers, including his friend Bjorn Riley, who narrowly missed out on an Olympic spot for 2024.\", \"from\": 6145, \"to\": 6367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6264, \"end\": 6272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999793981262, \"rank\": 2.035711181839277e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6302, \"end\": 6307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beorn_Estrithson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5647077646513088e-12, \"text\": \"Bjorn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beorn_Estrithson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beorn_Estrithson\"}, {\"begin\": 6308, \"end\": 6313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\", \"score\": 0.9984870148401341, \"rank\": 0.0015129913761136714, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Technologies\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amos\", \"from\": 6145, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"his success\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6169}, {\"ngram\": \"the fearless mentality\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6211}, {\"ngram\": \"his cadre\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6246}, {\"ngram\": \"his friend\", \"from\": 6291, \"to\": 6301}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic spot\", \"from\": 6342, \"to\": 6357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are the best bike handlers on the circuit-if you have those skills, you are not afraid to just fully commit to a descent and go for it,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 6369, \"to\": 6518, \"entities\": [], \"nou